Help Type: topic
Topic: command

Command Reference

Archive-first commands:
  import      Import source material into an archive at source stage.
  build       Build graph, summary, or ready stages from existing source data.
  estimate    Estimate words, token scale, calls, time, cost, and risk before build.
  status      Show archive readiness and object counts.
  index       Show the archive home/index page.
  ls          List chapters, nodes, edges, evidence, summaries, or metadata.
  find        Find objects by whitespace-separated keyword AND search.
  grep        Search objects for one exact continuous text phrase.
  page        Read one object by id.
  evidence    Show source evidence for an object.
  links       Show outgoing node links.
  backlinks   Show incoming node links.
  related     Show graph-adjacent knowledge units.
  path        Find a directed graph path between two nodes in one chapter.
  map         Print graph edges.
  pack        Pack deterministic context around a known object id.
  export      Export a projection from the archive.

Command shapes:
  spinedigest import <archive.sdpub> [source] [--input-format <format>]
  spinedigest build <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary|ready>] [--chapter <id>] [--confirm]
  spinedigest estimate <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary|ready>] [--json]
  spinedigest status <archive.sdpub> [--json]
  spinedigest index <archive.sdpub> [--json]
  spinedigest ls <archive.sdpub> [chapters|nodes|edges|evidence|summaries|meta] [--json]
  spinedigest find <archive.sdpub> <query> [--json]
  spinedigest grep <archive.sdpub> <query> [--json]
  spinedigest page <archive.sdpub> <id> [--json]
  spinedigest evidence <archive.sdpub> <id> [--json]
  spinedigest related <archive.sdpub> <node:id> [--json]
  spinedigest pack <archive.sdpub> <id> [--budget <chars>] [--json]
  spinedigest export <archive.sdpub> --output-format <format> [--output <path>]

Direct digest and maintenance:
  spinedigest transform [--input <path>] [--output <path>] [--input-format <format>] [--output-format <format>] [--digest-dir <path>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>] [--stage <planned|sourced|graphed|summarized>] [--verbose]
  spinedigest sdpub <subcommand> ...
  spinedigest config status [--llm <json>]

